cu.explanation_en: Setting the AMF IP to a malformed address (192.168.70.132.1) will cause IP parsing errors and prevent NG connection establishment.

du.explanation_en: Changing the NR cell ID from a number to a string will cause type validation errors during DU configuration parsing.
du.explanation_zh: 將 NR 小區 ID 從數字改為字串會在 DU 配置解析期間造成類型驗證錯誤。
